<div class="container mt-4">
    <h2>✅ Current Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Mobile-style design for a clean and simple workout tracking experience</li>
        <li>Exercise selection with categorized list</li>
        <li>Detailed set tracking (reps and weight)</li>
        <li>Finish Workout button that saves workout history</li>
        <li>View past workouts with full breakdown</li>
        <li>Local workout saving (even when not logged in)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">🛠 Coming Soon</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Password reset via email</li>
        <li>Progressive Web App (PWA) installation support on mobile</li>
        <li>Offline mode support for PWA</li>
        <li>User profile management (update email, password, delete account)</li>
        <li>Custom workout naming</li>
        <li>Workout notes</li>
        <li>Filtering and sorting of workout history</li>
        <li>Ability to favorite or repeat past workouts</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">🐞 Known Bugs / Issues</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Reset Password Emails Not Being Sent <STRONG>PLEASE WRITE DOWN YOUR PASSWORD FOR THE TIME BEING... THIS IS THE MAIN BUG RIGHT NOW</STRONG></li>
        <li>History page sometimes shows malformed or duplicate entries (edge cases)</li>
        <li>Back button behavior may be inconsistent on some mobile browsers</li>
        <li>Initial load time on first visit can take a few seconds</li>
        <li>Some button tap targets may be small on iOS Safari</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-4">
        If you spot any bugs or have suggestions, please reach out via email, LinkedIn, or Instagram. Your feedback helps shape ERND into the best version of itself.
    </p>
